These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 10

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-10-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, iced-tea, tea, juice
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, fishing, puzzles, hiking
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, metal, punk, soul
 1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who's hobby is reading##1
 2. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the left of the person drinking tea##8
 3. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the fan soul##3
 4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is not the fan metal##6
 5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the person drinking tea or the person who's hobby is puzzles is the fan punk, but not both##10
 6. the person drinking tea and the fan electronic have the same parity positions##9
 7. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the fan punk##3
 8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the left of the fan soul##5
 9. the person drinking tea is in an even position##4
10. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person drinking iced-tea and the fan electronic##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | tea   | juice      | iced-tea    |
| Hobby         | reading     | puzzles | fishing | hiking |
| Music-Genre   | punk       | electronic | soul         | metal     |

