.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-10-2::.
There 4 different types of food: onion, strawberry, apricot, broccoli
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, japanese, thai, turkish
4 different pets are kept: turtle, bird, mouse, rat
 1. the colombian is the person eating broccoli or the owner of the rat is the colombian, but not both##10
 2. the thai is somewhere to the left of the owner of the turtle##5
 3. the colombian is on the left or right of the person eating broccoli##3
 4. the owner of the mouse and the colombian have different parity positions##9
 5. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
 6. the owner of the rat is on the left or right of the owner of the turtle##3
 7. the owner of the rat is on the left or right of the thai##3
 8. the person eating apricot is on the left or right of the person eating onion##3
 9. the person eating onion is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
10. the owner of the turtle is not to the right of the owner of the bird##8
11. the turkish is in an even position##4
12. the colombian is the person eating onion or the colombian is the owner of the rat, but not both##10
13. the person eating onion is not to the right of the person eating apricot##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |    3    |    4    |
| Food          | broccoli | strawberry    | onion | apricot    |
| Nationality   | thai   | colombian | japanese  | turkish |
| Pet           | mouse     | rat    | turtle    | bird    |

