.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-10-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, 7up, iced-tea, almond-milk
There 4 different types of food: orange, peas, asparagus, zucchini
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, nigerian, turkish, french
1. the person eating zucchini is the argentine##1
2. the person eating asparagus is on the far right##1
3. the person eating zucchini is the french or the person eating zucchini is the person drinking 7up, but not both##10
4. the person eating asparagus is not to the right of the person drinking milk##8
5. the turkish is somewhere to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##5
6. the nigerian is between the person eating orange and the argentine##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |       3       |   4    |
| Beverage      | almond-milk         | iced-tea     | 7up | milk |
| Food          | orange | peas | zucchini         | asparagus   |
| Nationality   | turkish     | nigerian   | argentine       | french   |

