.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-10-4::.
There 4 different types of food: onion, nectarine, cherry, lettuce
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, traveling, skydiving, dancing
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, egyptian, brazilian, indonesian
 1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the egyptian##1
 2. the malaysian is not to the right of the person eating cherry##8
 3. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far left##1
 4. the person eating cherry is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 5. the person who's hobby is traveling is not the malaysian##6
 6. the egyptian is somewhere to the left of the person eating nectarine##5
 7. the person who's hobby is dancing is the brazilian or the person who's hobby is dancing is the person eating nectarine, but not both##10
 8. the brazilian is the person eating cherry or the brazilian is the person who's hobby is traveling, but not both##10
 9. the indonesian is somewhere between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person eating cherry##7
10. the indonesian is on the right of the person eating onion##1
11. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the indonesian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4    |
| Food          | lettuce  | onion   | nectarine | cherry  |
| Hobby         | gardening     | skydiving  | traveling | dancing |
| Nationality   | malaysian | egyptian | indonesian  | brazilian |

