.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-10-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, water, fanta, tea
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, martial-arts, epic, scientific
4 different pets are kept: horse, ferret, lizard, frog
 1. the person drinking water is in an odd position##4
 2. the owner of the horse is not the person watching martial-arts movies##6
 3. the owner of the ferret is between the person watching epic movies and the person watching comedy movies##2
 4. the person drinking water is not the person watching scientific movies##6
 5. the owner of the frog and the person watching comedy movies have different parity positions##9
 6. the person drinking milk is the person watching comedy movies or the person drinking milk is the owner of the horse, but not both##10
 7. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the right of the person drinking milk##5
 8. the person watching scientific movies is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
10. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the right of the person drinking tea##5
11. the owner of the lizard is somewhere between the person drinking fanta and the person drinking tea##7
12. the person drinking water is somewhere to the right of the person drinking milk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage      | milk   | tea | water | fanta   |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | martial-arts    | comedy   | scientific |
| Pet           | horse    | ferret | lizard    | frog  |

