 3. the person who's hobby is hiking is not to the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##8
 4. the person driving the jet-ski and the italian have different parity positions##9
 5. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 6. the italian is not to the left of the person driving the jet-ski##8
 7. the turkish is on the far right##1
 8. the canadian is somewhere between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the australian##7
 9. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
10. the italian is between the person driving the boat and the canadian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4    |
| Hobby         | fishing   | drawing | sudoku  | hiking |
| Nationality   | australian  | canadian      | italian | turkish |
| Transport     | snowmobile | jet-ski       | airplane    | boat   |

