.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-10-7::.
There 4 different types of food: peach, lemon, apricot, blueberry
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, journalist, musician, engineer
4 different pets are kept: turtle, cat, rabbit, snake
 1. the person eating blueberry is not to the left of the person eating apricot##8
 2. the coach is between the owner of the turtle and the person eating blueberry##2
 3. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the engineer##3
 4. the person eating blueberry is somewhere between the person eating lemon and the owner of the cat##7
 5. the owner of the cat and the person eating peach have the same parity positions##9
 6. the journalist is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 7. the musician is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3
 8. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person eating lemon##1
 9. the owner of the turtle is the coach or the owner of the turtle is the person eating apricot, but not both##10
10. the owner of the turtle and the journalist have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |       3        |     4      |
| Food   | apricot    | peach     | blueberry         | lemon |
| Job    | journalist | coach    | musician | engineer    |
| Pet    | turtle      | cat | rabbit            | snake   |

