 1. the person eating mango is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is camping##5
 2. the person who's hobby is camping is not to the right of the person watching zombie movies##8
 3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's hobby is camping is in an even position##4
 5. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching documentary movies##5
 6. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching superhero movies##5
 7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
 8. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere to the left of the person eating cabbage##5
 9. the person eating broccoli is not to the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##8
10. the person watching zombie movies is the person who's hobby is camping or the person who's hobby is camping is the person eating cherry, but not both##10
11. the person eating broccoli is on the left or right of the person watching superhero movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |    4    |
