The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, action, sports, musical
4 different pets are kept: goat, chinchilla, goldfish, bird
 1. the person watching musical movies is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3
 2. the owner of the chinchilla is the person watching sports movies or the owner of the chinchilla is the person eating banana, but not both##10
 3. the person eating broccoli is not to the right of the person watching action movies##8
 4. the person eating broccoli is not to the left of the owner of the chinchilla##8
 5. the person watching musical movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating artichoke##5
 6. the person eating broccoli is in an even position##4
 7. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
 8. the person eating artichoke is the owner of the goldfish##1
 9. the person watching sports movies is not to the right of the owner of the chinchilla##8
10. the owner of the goat is not the person watching musical movies##6
11. the person eating banana is somewhere to the left of the owner of the chinchilla##5
12. the person eating artichoke is somewhere to the left of the person watching sports movies##5
13. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
14. the person watching horror movies is not to the left of the owner of the goldfish##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |      4      |
| Food          | artichoke   | banana | potato  | broccoli        |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | musical      | sports    | action |
| Pet           | goldfish   | bird    | chinchilla | goat      |

 